<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>I have passed your responses to our Underwriting Team for review</b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please</span><b style="font-size: 12pt;"> allow 48 working hours for our reply</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">. We will, of course, endeavour to get back to you sooner.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please note, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">if the request should need to be referred to the insurer for approval, this can take slightly longer for a response</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>